{"TopicId":103533,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"How do I hide the navball and all those other things.","CreatedByName":"Seannaut","CreatedById":140552,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-06T16:28:42Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Seannaut","CreatedById":140552,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-06T16:28:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI need to hide the navball \u0026amp; stuff, do I require a mod or something? \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E:cool:\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E:cool:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E-Seannaut \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E:cool:\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E:cool:\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Red Iron Crown","CreatedById":12858,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-06T16:41:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EWelcome aboard!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EPress F2 to hide the GUI, no mods required.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"impyre","CreatedById":116031,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-06T16:59:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EJust FYI, \u003Ca href=\u0022http://wiki.kerbalspaceprogram.com/wiki/Key_bindings\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://wiki.kerbalspaceprogram.com/wiki/Key_bindings\u003C/a\u003E lists out all key bindings and even explains different keys for different systems. Most (if not all) of this info is also available in game through the options. So next time you\u0027re playing, if you need to figure out a key, you can check there without having to alt-tab.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Taki117","CreatedById":89975,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-06T17:01:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EYou can also click the arrow on top of the navball, if you only want to hide the navball.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stone Blue","CreatedById":77721,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-06T17:46:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI know this is a mod, but might be worth also looking at:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EEnhanced NavBall\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/50524-0-90-Enhanced-Navball-1-3\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/50524-0-90-Enhanced-Navball-1-3\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Seannaut","CreatedById":140552,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-07T04:52:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Red Iron Crown\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Red Iron Crown\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EWelcome aboard!\u003Cp\u003EPress F2 to hide the GUI, no mods required.\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThanks!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Stone Blue\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Stone Blue\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EI know this is a mod, but might be worth also looking at:\u003Cp\u003EEnhanced NavBall\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/50524-0-90-Enhanced-Navball-1-3\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/50524-0-90-Enhanced-Navball-1-3\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003ESweet! I\u0027ll check it out!\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ip